    "description": "<p>You create an enchanted flame that surrounds your hand and produces no heat, but sheds bright light in a 20-foot radius around you and dim light for an additional 20 feet. Only you and up to 6 creatures of your choice can see this light.</p><hr class=\"a5e-rule u-my-md\"><p><strong>Rare: Transferrable Darklight.</strong> During the spell\u2019s duration, you can use an action to kindle this light on a willing creature\u2019s hand, sharing the effect with them. When the spell\u2019s duration ends, or when any of the flames are dispelled, the spell ends.</p>",
